1
00:00:01,110 --> 00:00:03,950
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,190
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:16,010 --> 00:00:18,360
Miss, that's dangerous!

5
00:00:20,630 --> 00:00:21,910
Phew, that was close...

6
00:00:23,510 --> 00:00:25,620
I haven't been able to find any decent jobs.

7
00:00:25,870 --> 00:00:28,320
What am I going to do 
about this month's rent?

8
00:00:30,220 --> 00:00:31,980
"It'll work out somehow?"

9
00:00:33,750 --> 00:00:36,260
I never realized you had such 
a positive outlook, Plue.

10
00:02:16,050 --> 00:02:17,740
No one's here...

11
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:21,400
And why exactly do I get so 
tense every time I come home?

12
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:25,120
Yeah, I have been through a lot.

13
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:27,410
Anyway, time for a bath!

14
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:31,780
It's like I'm back from the dead!

15
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,900
Hey, who're you callin' dead?!

16
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:38,040
Comedy doesn't work so well 
when I'm doing both parts...

17
00:02:40,260 --> 00:02:44,130
Wow, you actually do wilt if 
you get soaked in hot water.

18
00:02:45,780 --> 00:02:47,320
How cute!

19
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:52,120
Battle of Fairy Tail!

20
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:00,370
Good night!

21
00:03:04,780 --> 00:03:07,200
Somethin' seems familiar here...

22
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,830
Good morning, Lucy.

23
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:15,770
One: I'm over here!

24
00:03:15,770 --> 00:03:17,100
Two: This is <i>my</i> house!

25
00:03:17,100 --> 00:03:18,450
Three: That is <i>my</i> bed!

26
00:03:18,450 --> 00:03:19,050
Aye...

27
00:03:19,170 --> 00:03:20,550
Get out!

28
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:22,250
Nope, not happenin'...

29
00:03:23,210 --> 00:03:24,430
Is he even listening?

30
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:27,410
Give Natsu back his scarf...

31
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:32,190
Now that you mention it, I 
never see him without it, do I?

32
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:36,650
He said that he got it from Igneel.

33
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:43,630
Hey, is Natsu really okay?

34
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,390
Yeah.

35
00:03:44,390 --> 00:03:48,090
This is a side effect from 
when he ate Etherion.

36
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:49,330
Oh, it is?

37
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:54,100
Aye. He got this way before when 
he ate Laxus's lightning once.

38
00:03:54,450 --> 00:03:57,640
I guess eating magic other than 
fire isn't any good for him.

39
00:03:57,640 --> 00:04:00,140
And wait, why did he eat Laxus's lightning?

40
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:03,010
Natsu challenged him in the past.

41
00:04:03,010 --> 00:04:05,110
Although he was wiped out 
instantly, of course.

42
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:11,140
Laxus is seriously that powerful?

43
00:04:11,390 --> 00:04:13,800
Aye! He's really majorly strong.

44
00:04:14,180 --> 00:04:17,090
Although there's Erza and Mystogan too...

45
00:04:17,090 --> 00:04:19,590
Mira used to be really dangerous herself.

46
00:04:19,590 --> 00:04:21,310
She was called the "Demon."

47
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:22,570
Mira-san was what?

48
00:04:22,570 --> 00:04:27,910
I wonder who would win if Fairy Tail held 
a contest to see who was the strongest?

49
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:32,260
I don't want us fellow wizards 
to be ranked like that.

50
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:34,470
There's also Gray and Elfman...

51
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:36,700
Gajeel and Juvia are obviously strong too...

52
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:37,820
Sure, whatever.

53
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:39,240
Everyone's awesome...

54
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,390
Anyway, see you tomorrow!

55
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,490
Aye...

56
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:44,890
What's this?

57
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:47,790
I was thinking about giving it to you.

58
00:04:47,790 --> 00:04:48,970
You need the money, right?

59
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:52,930
Fairy Tail is participating 
in the Harvest Festival.

60
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:56,350
Look at the bottom right.

61
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:59,890
Miss Fairy Tail Contest?

62
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:00,400
Aye!

63
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:04,280
The prize for winning is 500,000 jewel!

64
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:05,760
500,000?

65
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:08,760
That's seven month's worth of 
rent! And it's perfect for me!

66
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:12,370
Mira and Cana are participating, 
but I don't think you'd lose, Lucy.

67
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,130
Mira-san, too?

68
00:05:15,130 --> 00:05:18,100
She used to do photo spreads 
for the Weekly Sorcerer...

69
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:21,790
But I'm younger!

70
00:05:21,790 --> 00:05:23,860
So with my fresh new charm...

71
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:25,500
I can do this!

72
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:27,890
I can get that 500,000!

73
00:05:27,890 --> 00:05:30,220
I'm gonna win this thing! Oh, yeah!

74
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:34,720
Didn't you say something about not wanting 
your fellow wizards ranked like that?

75
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:37,290
Happy, would you like a yummy fish?

76
00:05:37,290 --> 00:05:40,530
Natsu... So this is what 
they call human ego...

77
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:46,110
This is the town of Shirotsume.

78
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:51,240
The Dark Guild, Ghoul Spirit 
is to the north-west.

79
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:57,550
You laughed at us?

80
00:05:57,710 --> 00:05:59,760
You came for a beating, you punks!

81
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,500
Don't let them leave here alive!

82
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:05,410
Honestly, what does a guild like 
yours that sneaks among the shadows

83
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:08,170
think they are doing making 
fun of an official guild...

84
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,710
What happened?

85
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:12,640
They turned to stone?

86
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:15,640
Get 'em!

87
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:20,230
Go now, my babies!

88
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:30,040
That's enough, Bickslow.

89
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:32,370
What? That's it?

90
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:37,000
How dare they form a guild, 
as weak as they are.

91
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:40,960
My babies ain't had enough fun yet!

92
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:41,860
More!

93
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:42,960
More!

94
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:46,130
Then I've got something perfect for you...

95
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:50,390
Oh, you mean what Laxus was talking about?

96
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:51,890
He's finally going to do it.

97
00:06:52,930 --> 00:06:56,780
I've been waiting for this moment forever!

98
00:06:56,780 --> 00:06:58,520
So have my babies!

99
00:06:59,890 --> 00:07:04,780
Just three of them completely wiped 
us... wiped Ghoul Spirit out!

100
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:10,920
That's Fairy Tail's Raijin 
Tribe... Laxus's personal guard!

101
00:07:14,150 --> 00:07:16,770
My Raijin Tribe is coming back.

102
00:07:16,770 --> 00:07:19,170
Finally, my moment has come.

103
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:23,150
Time for the Fairies to destroy each other.

104
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:28,010
Old man, your time is over!

105
00:07:32,030 --> 00:07:35,180
The whole city is focused 
on the Harvest Festival...

106
00:07:35,180 --> 00:07:38,260
Everyone said they're busy 
preparing for the Fantasia.

107
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:43,950
Yes, since this is Fairy Tail's grand parade 
that's the pride of the entire continent!

108
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:46,060
It'd be nice if Laxus would participate.

109
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,490
Enough about him.

110
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:52,950
I heard from Levy that he's returned to town.

111
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,360
He's what?

112
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:58,680
Master...

113
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:03,130
He had to come back now, of all times...

114
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:06,480
Gramps, Gramps!

115
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,810
Gramps!

116
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:10,160
Oh, Laxus!

117
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,850
Aren't you going to join the Fantasia?

118
00:08:12,850 --> 00:08:16,470
I promised to watch it with you, remember?

119
00:08:16,470 --> 00:08:18,470
Yay, yay!

120
00:08:20,490 --> 00:08:23,640
I hope I can join Fairy Tail soon!

121
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:26,110
Not so fast there, kiddo!

122
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:32,420
I-I can't see!

123
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:33,900
No kidding...

124
00:08:39,490 --> 00:08:41,900
How 'bout that, Laxus?

125
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:44,950
Those are Fairy Tail wizards!

126
00:08:44,950 --> 00:08:46,120
Wow!

127
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,000
Wow, Gramps!

128
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:51,260
You're the best guild master ever!

129
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:58,260
When I grow up, I want to join Fairy Tail!

130
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,080
I see, I see!

131
00:09:05,260 --> 00:09:08,690
And then, the day of the Harvest Festival...

132
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:12,020
It's a festival!

133
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:12,990
Aye!

134
00:09:12,990 --> 00:09:14,030
Time to chow down!

135
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:16,180
Gotta eat 'em all!

136
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:17,950
Let's eat!

137
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:21,830
He still doesn't seem so well.

138
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:23,740
Is he okay?

139
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:25,870
Just leave him be...

140
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:27,400
You never change, do you?

141
00:09:28,830 --> 00:09:29,920
Warren!

142
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,330
How long has it been?

143
00:09:31,330 --> 00:09:34,010
I made it back for the 
Harvest Festival, somehow.

144
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:37,090
You take on too many jobs at once, man!

145
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:38,440
Wow!

146
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:41,020
I'm the new recruit, Juvia.

147
00:09:41,020 --> 00:09:43,530
Oh, I've heard about you.

148
00:09:43,530 --> 00:09:45,090
Warren Rocko.

149
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:47,250
He has telepathic abilities.

150
00:09:47,250 --> 00:09:48,260
Nice to meet you.

151
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:50,330
Nice to meet you as well.

152
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,190
But...

153
00:09:52,930 --> 00:09:54,830
What a lot of people!

154
00:09:54,830 --> 00:09:59,100
People have come from all 
over to see the Fantasia.

155
00:09:59,100 --> 00:10:00,890
I want to see it too!

156
00:10:00,890 --> 00:10:02,650
You're participating in it, remember?

157
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:04,970
Oh, yeah! That reminds me...

158
00:10:04,970 --> 00:10:07,460
The Miss Fairy Tail Contest is starting!

159
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:08,920
My rent!

160
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:13,280
Juvia cannot allow herself 
to lose to Lucy-san.

161
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,030
You're going to participate too?

162
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:19,560
Everyone, I'm so glad you could make it!

163
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:21,590
The battle of beauty between 
our female Fairies...

164
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:25,390
Let's start the Miss Fairy Tail Contest!

165
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:29,980
I am Max, the sand wizard, 
and I will be your host!

166
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,860
You don't care about this stuff, right?

167
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:36,110
I'm a Man!

168
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:38,230
Entry number one:

169
00:10:38,230 --> 00:10:42,370
The exotic beauty with a 
bottomless pit for a stomach,

170
00:10:43,410 --> 00:10:45,910
Cana Alberona!

171
00:10:48,410 --> 00:10:52,280
Now it's time to appeal to 
the audience with your magic!

172
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:58,760
The cards are hiding Cana's body...

173
00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:01,880
She changed into a swimsuit!

174
00:11:02,460 --> 00:11:04,700
I'll take that beer-money, thanks.

175
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,070
A swimsuit?

176
00:11:07,070 --> 00:11:07,870
No fair!

177
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,890
I see...

178
00:11:08,890 --> 00:11:10,380
That's a good idea.

179
00:11:10,380 --> 00:11:11,800
You're participating too, Erza?

180
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:15,270
When I hear there's a contest, 
I can't help but get motivated.

181
00:11:15,270 --> 00:11:17,440
My rent is slipping away from me...

182
00:11:17,690 --> 00:11:19,670
Entry number two:

183
00:11:19,670 --> 00:11:22,900
She might be a newcomer, but 
her abilities are S class!

184
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:25,900
Rain or shine, this woman 
will steal your heart!

185
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:29,000
Juvia Lockser!

186
00:11:29,370 --> 00:11:34,480
May these feelings reach you, Gray-sama!

187
00:11:37,830 --> 00:11:40,510
She put on a performance 
that matches her swimsuit!

188
00:11:41,010 --> 00:11:44,640
Gray-sama, did you see?

189
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,950
Another one going for sex appeal?!

190
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:50,020
Entry number three:

191
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:52,140
Everyone's favorite poster 
girl of the guild...

192
00:11:52,140 --> 00:11:55,770
Her beauty is known throughout the land!

193
00:11:56,770 --> 00:11:58,940
Mirajane!

194
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,540
We've been waiting!

195
00:11:58,940 --> 00:12:00,160
We have a winner!

196
00:11:59,540 --> 00:12:00,940
It's really her!

197
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:02,160
She's cuter in person!

198
00:12:00,940 --> 00:12:03,200
Now, appeal to the audience!

199
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:07,320
My specialty is transformation 
magic, so I'll transform!

200
00:12:09,660 --> 00:12:11,700
Head-only Happy! Aye!

201
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:16,340
Head-only Gajeel-kun!

202
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:20,530
You're the only one happy 
about this, you know.

203
00:12:20,530 --> 00:12:21,740
Neechan...

204
00:12:22,980 --> 00:12:25,220
The crowd favorite just 
shot herself in the foot.

205
00:12:25,810 --> 00:12:27,640
Entry number four:

206
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:30,320
She needs no explanation... Titania!

207
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,530
That's my cue!

208
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:36,430
Erza Scarlet!

209
00:12:35,530 --> 00:12:36,430
She's here!

210
00:12:36,430 --> 00:12:38,190
Erza, you're so cool!

211
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:38,830
Fairy Tail's strongest woman!

212
00:12:38,830 --> 00:12:40,570
She's really popular!

213
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:44,930
I will show you all a very special requip.

214
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:55,820
G-Goth Loli?

215
00:12:56,460 --> 00:12:57,800
That decided it.

216
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,220
That's really <i>different</i> of her.

217
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:01,170
Oui...

218
00:13:01,170 --> 00:13:03,360
Entry number five!

219
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:07,120
The little fairy with 
cutes and intelligence...

220
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:09,090
Levy McGarden!

221
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,450
Levy!

222
00:13:11,450 --> 00:13:13,390
Solid Script!

223
00:13:17,450 --> 00:13:19,060
Levy!

224
00:13:19,310 --> 00:13:21,480
Entry number six:

225
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:26,300
The sexy sniper Bisca Moulin!

226
00:13:30,350 --> 00:13:31,750
Requip!

227
00:13:33,260 --> 00:13:36,150
The Gunner!

228
00:13:36,330 --> 00:13:38,220
Yeehaw!

229
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:40,770
How cute!

230
00:13:40,770 --> 00:13:42,180
Everyone's really amazing...

231
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,430
Entry number seven:

232
00:13:44,430 --> 00:13:46,620
Our guild's super rookie!

233
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:47,730
That's me!

234
00:13:47,730 --> 00:13:50,750
This upcoming star will sparkle with 
the guidance of Celestial Spirits!

235
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:52,370
Lucy Heart-

236
00:13:52,370 --> 00:13:54,430
Don't say my last name!

237
00:13:54,430 --> 00:13:55,440
What's this?

238
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,630
She's cute...

239
00:13:56,880 --> 00:14:00,210
If they found out who my dad is, 
they'll never award me the 500,000!

240
00:14:00,210 --> 00:14:02,230
Now, appeal to the audience!

241
00:14:02,230 --> 00:14:05,830
Um, I'm going to do a cheer 
dance routine with my Spirits!

242
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:09,200
Entry number eight:

243
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:11,660
Hey! I'm not done appealing yet!

244
00:14:11,900 --> 00:14:14,440
If you want a Fairy, then you want me.

245
00:14:15,110 --> 00:14:17,350
If you want beauty, then you want me.

246
00:14:17,610 --> 00:14:20,910
Yes, I am all you want!

247
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:25,950
The winner is obviously me, Evergreen!

248
00:14:25,950 --> 00:14:29,210
Okay! The idiotic contest is now over!

249
00:14:30,190 --> 00:14:31,650
Evergreen?

250
00:14:31,950 --> 00:14:33,430
She's back?

251
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:44,400
Hey, don't get in my way!

252
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:46,610
My rent is counting on this, you know!

253
00:14:46,610 --> 00:14:48,740
Lucy, don't look into her eyes!

254
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:51,630
What's with this kid?

255
00:14:55,950 --> 00:14:56,940
What's this?

256
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,620
She's turned to stone!

257
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:58,010
Is this supposed to be appealing?

258
00:14:58,010 --> 00:14:59,060
This is bad...

259
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:01,120
Everyone, quickly escape!

260
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:06,640
What are you doing, Evergreen?

261
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:08,630
Do you plan on ruining the festival?

262
00:15:10,380 --> 00:15:13,220
You need some entertainment 
for a festival, yes?

263
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:16,600
Neechan!

264
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,640
Even Erza!

265
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:19,150
You fool!

266
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:21,270
Return them to normal at once!

267
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:29,110
Hey, you Fairy Fails!

268
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:31,610
This festival's just getting started!

269
00:15:31,610 --> 00:15:33,250
Laxus?

270
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,390
Freed?

271
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:37,200
Bickslow?

272
00:15:37,450 --> 00:15:38,820
The Raijin Tribe...

273
00:15:38,820 --> 00:15:40,500
Laxus's personal guard!

274
00:15:41,070 --> 00:15:43,520
Let's play, old man.

275
00:15:43,940 --> 00:15:46,000
Enough of this foolishness!

276
00:15:46,250 --> 00:15:48,230
Return them to normal at once!

277
00:15:48,230 --> 00:15:51,750
I wonder how many will be 
left to be in the Fantasia?

278
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:53,790
Don't!

279
00:15:57,100 --> 00:16:00,020
These women are my hostages.

280
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:03,700
If you break the rules, I'll 
shatter them, one by one.

281
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:04,890
I told you, remember?

282
00:16:04,890 --> 00:16:06,280
This is entertainment!

283
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:08,900
This isn't funny, Laxus!

284
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,950
I'm being serious.

285
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:16,350
Let's just see who the 
strongest is in Fairy Tail.

286
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:18,190
Time for fun!

287
00:16:18,190 --> 00:16:19,580
Fun, fun!

288
00:16:19,830 --> 00:16:21,490
The rules are simple!

289
00:16:21,490 --> 00:16:23,710
That last one standing is the winner!

290
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:27,530
Battle of Fairy Tail!

291
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:32,070
I like it! Simple!

292
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:33,380
I'm getting fired up!

293
00:16:33,890 --> 00:16:38,070
I like that eager spirit of yours.

294
00:16:38,070 --> 00:16:39,300
Natsu!

295
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:41,000
It's a festival, Gramps.

296
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,140
Let's do this.

297
00:16:42,140 --> 00:16:46,030
Don't you remember when you 
got beat by Laxus before?

298
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:47,630
I was just a kid!

299
00:16:47,630 --> 00:16:49,440
It was last year!

300
00:16:49,690 --> 00:16:52,200
I was a kid last year.

301
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:56,310
But I hate that you have no sense of flair.

302
00:16:56,310 --> 00:16:57,870
So cool down.

303
00:16:58,570 --> 00:16:59,700
Natsu!

304
00:16:59,700 --> 00:17:00,950
See what I said?

305
00:17:00,950 --> 00:17:01,950
What a Man...

306
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:06,980
Aww, and he had just recovered...

307
00:17:06,980 --> 00:17:11,820
If you want these girls returned 
to normal, you must defeat us!

308
00:17:11,820 --> 00:17:15,670
There are 4 of us, and 
around 100 of you, right?

309
00:17:15,670 --> 00:17:17,470
100 on 4!

310
00:17:17,470 --> 00:17:19,890
You have 3 hours.

311
00:17:19,890 --> 00:17:23,410
After that, they turn to dust, I'm afraid.

312
00:17:24,020 --> 00:17:27,150
The field of battle is 
the entirety of Magnolia.

313
00:17:27,150 --> 00:17:29,810
When you find us, the battle begins.

314
00:17:30,390 --> 00:17:32,330
Laxus...

315
00:17:32,610 --> 00:17:35,210
Stop this foolishness!

316
00:17:35,210 --> 00:17:37,670
Now, now! I said to cool down!

317
00:17:37,670 --> 00:17:39,540
It's entertainment for the festival, see?

318
00:17:40,450 --> 00:17:42,220
Let's have fun!

319
00:17:43,330 --> 00:17:46,730
Battle of Fairy Tail... Begin!

320
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:50,040
H-He disappeared!

321
00:17:50,040 --> 00:17:52,490
So we have to play tag in Magnolia?

322
00:17:52,670 --> 00:17:54,010
Damn it!

323
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:56,520
We have to save my sister and the others!

324
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:58,010
Get Laxus!

325
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:05,240
Bisca, I'll save you. Just you wait.

326
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:11,300
That fool...

327
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:14,660
I'll... I'll stop you!

328
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,360
Gramps!

329
00:18:17,610 --> 00:18:19,400
An invisible wall?

330
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,300
Don't be silly!

331
00:18:20,300 --> 00:18:21,720
There's nothing there!

332
00:18:23,370 --> 00:18:24,850
What's going on?

333
00:18:26,410 --> 00:18:27,650
What's this?

334
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:30,240
There are characters floating in the air...

335
00:18:30,710 --> 00:18:33,170
Freed's runes?

336
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,250
Runes?

337
00:18:35,250 --> 00:18:36,950
A type of barrier.

338
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:39,900
Anyone who steps in its boundary 
is bound by the rules.

339
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:42,050
If you don't obey them, you can't get out.

340
00:18:42,050 --> 00:18:43,220
Establishment Magic!

341
00:18:43,800 --> 00:18:45,350
What's written?

342
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:49,950
Those older than 80 or 
stone statues may not pass.

343
00:18:50,390 --> 00:18:53,110
A magic where the guy 
who sets the rules wins?

344
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:56,400
It takes a long time to write the runes.

345
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:59,910
It is not suited for a sudden battle,

346
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:03,520
but when it comes to setting 
traps, there's nothing better.

347
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:05,780
Can't you break it down, Gramps?

348
00:19:06,060 --> 00:19:08,750
The rune's rules are absolute!

349
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:11,710
Man, they planned for everything.

350
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:15,170
So I guess we'll have to handle it ourselves.

351
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:16,900
Gray...

352
00:19:16,900 --> 00:19:20,040
I don't care if he's your grandson 
or whatever, I ain't holdin' back.

353
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:21,650
I'll get Laxus.

354
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:28,100
Is there anyone who could beat Laxus?

355
00:19:28,850 --> 00:19:30,890
Erza might be able to...

356
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:33,570
But in her condition...

357
00:19:37,330 --> 00:19:38,210
Who's there?

358
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:40,590
Reedus?

359
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:43,160
I-I'm scared of Laxus...

360
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,550
Fine, fine...

361
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:47,820
Instead, I'd like you to pay a visit 
to Poluchka in the East Forest.

362
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:48,630
Oui?

363
00:19:48,630 --> 00:19:51,500
She might have some potion 
that'll cure petrification.

364
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,410
Oui.

365
00:19:56,430 --> 00:19:57,600
You're awake!

366
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,360
Huh?

367
00:19:58,360 --> 00:19:59,700
Where's Laxus?

368
00:19:59,700 --> 00:20:01,130
And wait, everyone's gone!

369
00:20:03,210 --> 00:20:06,430
If Natsu really got serious, then perhaps...

370
00:20:06,930 --> 00:20:09,430
Gramps, where did everyone go?

371
00:20:10,050 --> 00:20:13,270
Should I count on his latent ability?

372
00:20:13,810 --> 00:20:15,080
Natsu!

373
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,850
The festival has started!

374
00:20:16,850 --> 00:20:19,600
Laxus is somewhere within Magnolia!

375
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,800
Get out there and beat 'im!

376
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:24,630
All right!

377
00:20:24,630 --> 00:20:26,100
Just you wait, Laxus!

378
00:20:28,150 --> 00:20:29,350
Why?

379
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:31,900
Find them, Alzack?

380
00:20:31,900 --> 00:20:33,320
They aren't here.

381
00:20:33,320 --> 00:20:34,000
How about you?

382
00:20:34,250 --> 00:20:35,940
No, not a clue.

383
00:20:35,940 --> 00:20:36,750
Damn it!

384
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:38,660
How dare they do that to Bisca!

385
00:20:38,660 --> 00:20:40,720
Hey, calm down Alzack!

386
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:42,280
How can I be calm at a time like this?

387
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:43,850
We only have three hours!

388
00:20:46,090 --> 00:20:46,980
What's this?

389
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:48,160
Shoot!

390
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,400
Runes?

391
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:52,020
So there are rune traps around the city?

392
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:53,890
This must be Freed's work!

393
00:20:57,300 --> 00:21:03,780
Only the strongest wizard is 
allowed to exit these runes?

394
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:06,170
He's trying to make us fight each other?

395
00:21:06,170 --> 00:21:08,010
That's cruel, Freed!

396
00:21:08,620 --> 00:21:09,530
Sorry...

397
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:13,810
I... need to save Bisca!

398
00:21:14,740 --> 00:21:16,710
What's going on here?

399
00:21:16,710 --> 00:21:19,080
Natsu! Are you 80 years old?

400
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:19,900
Are you a stone statue?

401
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:21,200
As if!

402
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:25,630
Current Status Report.

403
00:21:26,850 --> 00:21:29,760
Jet vs. Droy vs. Alzack?

404
00:21:30,010 --> 00:21:31,760
W-What's this?

405
00:21:32,010 --> 00:21:34,630
Why are they fighting each other?

406
00:21:39,230 --> 00:21:41,900
Falcon Heaven's Soar!

407
00:21:43,410 --> 00:21:45,150
Knuckle Plant!

408
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:51,660
Guns Magic!

409
00:21:51,660 --> 00:21:53,910
Tornado Shot!

410
00:21:57,030 --> 00:21:59,100
Winner: Alzack.

411
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:02,100
Jet and Droy: Out of action.

412
00:22:02,100 --> 00:22:03,030
What?

413
00:22:08,780 --> 00:22:10,480
Damn... I'm sorry.

414
00:22:12,910 --> 00:22:18,140
I wonder how long you can stand to see the 
Fairies destroying each other, old man...

415
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:23,400
The hell with this, Laxus!

416
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:33,690
That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"

417
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:43,870
we even kindly overlooked the little lies.

418
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:49,970
If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.

419
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:58,720
Because I'll protect that smile.

420
00:22:59,100 --> 00:23:03,160
The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...

421
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:05,610
All the things I don't want to lose...

422
00:23:05,610 --> 00:23:10,290
Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.

423
00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:15,440
I just want to see you by my side,

424
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:21,070
all my happiness and sadness.

425
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:23,550
Let's start from here.

426
00:23:23,550 --> 00:23:26,150
Let's start our tomorrow.

427
00:23:26,150 --> 00:23:30,650
Let's do it like we've just been reborn.

428
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:36,200
Like flowers blown in a summer wind,

429
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:44,900
let us bloom brightly in this instant.

430
00:23:56,380 --> 00:23:58,720
It's finally time for the Raijin 
Tribe to enter the fight!

431
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:01,300
Evergreen, Bickslow, Freed...

432
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:03,600
Those guys are crazy strong, you know!

433
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,450
I'm gettin' fired up!

434
00:24:05,450 --> 00:24:07,730
Natsu, sorry to kill your excitement,

435
00:24:07,730 --> 00:24:11,400
but unless you can get out of 
the barrier, you can't join in.

436
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:13,470
Oh, right...

437
00:24:13,820 --> 00:24:16,810
Next time: Defeat your Friends 
to Save your Friends!

438
00:24:16,810 --> 00:24:20,080
Now that you mention it, Gajeel doesn't 
seem to be able to exit the barrier either.

439
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:22,180
Why don't you get to know each 
other better over a cup of tea?

440
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:24,180
Tea with him? No way!

